# InvoiceCalls.http
//second commit
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/invoices
@invoiceId = 1
@secondInvoiceId = 2
@visitId = 4
@petOwnerId = 2

### login Receptionist
POST http://localhost:8080/loginJWT
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "password": "password123"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));
    client.log("token: " + response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));
%}

### 1. Crear una Factura (createInvoice) EJECUTAR 2 VECES
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "invoiceDate": "2025-11-20",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "status": "UNPAID",
  "petOwnerId": {{petOwnerId}},
  "items": [
    {
      "description": "Annual Check-up",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 80.00,
      "itemTotal": 80.00
    },
    {
      "description": "Vaccination",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 70.00,
      "itemTotal": 70.00
    }
  ],
  "payments": []
}

### 2. Obtener una Factura por ID (getInvoice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 3. Listar todas las Facturas (listInvoices)
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 4. Actualizar una Factura (updateInvoice)
# Nota: Este endpoint solo actualiza totalAmount, discount y status.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{invoiceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "totalAmount": 160.00,
  "status": "UNPAID"
}

### 5. Procesar un Pago para una Factura (processPayment)
# Asumiendo que PaymentMethod es un Enum (e.g., CARD, CASH, TRANSFER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{invoiceId}}/payments?amountPaid=159.76&paymentMethod=CARD
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 6. Eliminar una Factura (deleteInvoice) DEBE DAR 422 SI SE HA PAGADO ALGO Y DEBE DAR 204 SIN NO HAY PAGOS
# **ADVERTENCIA:** Solo funciona si no tiene pagos registrados.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

//HAY QUE IR A VETERINARY CALLS E INICIAR Y TERMINAR UNA VISITA PARA QUE FUNCIONE
### 7. Generar Factura desde una Visita (generateInvoiceFromVisit)
# Requiere que la visita {{visitId}} exista y tenga el estado 'Completed'.
POST {{baseUrl}}/from-visit/{{visitId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 8. Generar Factura desde una Visita (generateInvoiceFromVisit) SIN COMPLETAR
# Requiere que la visita 1 exista y tenga el estado 'Completed'.
POST {{baseUrl}}/from-visit/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 9. Aplicar Descuento Manual (applyManualDiscount)
# Aplica un 10% de descuento manual a la factura {{invoiceId}}.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{secondInvoiceId}}/apply-discount?percentage=10.0
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 10. Crear una Venta de Medicación (createMedicationSale)
# Requiere que la medicación con ID 1 y 2 existan.
POST {{baseUrl}}/medication-sale?petOwnerId={{petOwnerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

[
  {
    "medicationId": 1,
    "quantity": 2
  },
  {
    "medicationId": 2,
    "quantity": 1
  }
]

